Figure¶

In [1]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

Mt figure nh ta thng thy l mt i tng ca lp figure trong th vin matplotlib. Lp figure c nh ngha trong module matplotlib.figure, lp ny cha tt c nhng thnh phn ca mt hnh v (top level container for all plot elements). Tc l mi thuc tnh, phng thc ca hnh v u c nh ngha trong lp ny.

khi to mt figure trng, ta ch n gin gi phng thc .figure() ca plt

Khi to figure trng:

fig = plt.figure()

Gi phng thc show() ca pyplot hin figure hin ti:

plt.show()

Khi , bin fig tr thnh mt th hin ca lp figure. S

Sau khi khi to, fig ch l mt reference n mt i tng thc s trn RAM. xut hin ca s figure, thng thng ta gi lnh plt.show():

In [2]:
fig = plt.figure()
plt.show()

<Figure size 432x288 with 0 Axes>

Nh vy, v mt trc quan th figure l ci ca s cha tt c nhng g ta s v trn .

Thành phần chính của một figure:¶

Thnh phn chnh ca mt figure l cc axes (nhng khung nh hn v hnh ln ). Mt figure c th cha mt hoc nhiu axes . Ni cch khc, figure ch l khung cha, chnh cc axes mi tht s l ni cc hnh v c v ln.

Theo ngn ng i tng th: figure c mt thuc tnh kiu list gi l axes. Danh sch ny cha cc axes ca figure . Mi axes l mt i tng ca lp Axes (lp ny c nh ngha trong module matplotlib.axes). Mi axes c th cha mt hoc nhiu hnh v (plots).

Nh vy, cc phn t nh: ng v (plots), cc im chia (ticks), tn ca cc trc ta (xlabel, ylabel), u l con ca axes ch khng phi l ca figure. V th, s khng c nhng methods gi t figure kiu nh:

  • fig.plot()
  • fig.get_xlabel()
  • fig.set_xticks()

V d ca mt figure c nhiu axes chng cho nhau:

In [3]:
# Khi to mt figure trng
fig1 = plt.figure(u'Cc axes chng cho nhau trong mt figure')

# Thm axes bng lnh add_subplot
fig1.add_subplot(1,1,1, facecolor='white')

# Thm axes bng lnh add_axes
fig1.add_axes([0.1, 0.4, 0.4, 0.3], facecolor=(0,0,1))
fig1.add_axes([0.6, 0.2, 0.4, 0.3], facecolor='#ff0000')

# Thm tip mt axes bng lnh add_subplot
# Vit tt ca fig1.add_subplot(1,3,2):
fig1.add_subplot(132, facecolor=(0,0,0,0.5))

# Hin hnh v ln
# fig1.show()
Out[3]:
<matplotlib.axes._subplots.AxesSubplot at 0x1bc3d9f7070>

Trong thc t khng ai b tr cc axes nh vy. V d trn ch cho thy: mt figure c th c bao nhiu axes ty thch, c th thm-xa-sa cc axes bt k lc no v chng l cc i tng c lp (chng ta thy trong mi axes, cc trc ta lun l t 0 n 1).

Quản lí các axes trong figure¶

Tt c cc axes ca figure u c lit k trong fig1.axes ( v d trn), nhng danh sch ny l Read-only. V th ly danh sch cc axes v thay i chng, ta phi dng phng thc get_axes() ca fig1 (iu ny khng c g l nu c kinh nghim vi OOP).

Gi s by gi mun b ht cc im chia ta i, thm vo mi axes dng ch TEXmath gc di bn tri. Ch cn dng vng lp for nh sau:

In [4]:
# Khi to mt figure trng
fig1 = plt.figure(u'Cc axes chng cho nhau trong mt figure')

# Thm axes bng lnh add_subplot
fig1.add_subplot(1,1,1, facecolor='white')

# Thm axes bng lnh add_axes
fig1.add_axes([0.1, 0.4, 0.4, 0.3], facecolor=(0,0,1))
fig1.add_axes([0.6, 0.2, 0.4, 0.3], facecolor='#ff0000')

# Thm tip mt axes bng lnh add_subplot
# Vit tt ca fig1.add_subplot(1,3,2):
fig1.add_subplot(132, facecolor=(0,0,0,0.5))

for ax in fig1.get_axes():
    ax.set_alpha(0.5)
    ax.set_xticks([ ])
    ax.set_yticks([ ])
    ax.text(0,0,"TEXmath", {'fontsize':14})

Figure size¶

Thuc tnh ny quy nh kch thc ca s figure (theo n v inch)

In [5]:
fig = plt.figure( figsize = (8, 4), dpi = 100 )

<Figure size 800x400 with 0 Axes>

Cc i s tng t cng c th c truyn cho cc layout managers, chng hn nh hm subplots:

In [6]:
x = np.linspace(0, 5, 11)
y = x ** 2
In [7]:
fig, axes = plt.subplots(figsize = (12, 3))

axes.plot(x, y, 'r')
axes.set_xlabel('x')
axes.set_ylabel('y')
axes.set_title('title')
Out[7]:
Text(0.5, 1.0, 'title')

Một số thuộc tính khác:¶

  • edgecolor quy nh mu ca khung vin bao quanh tt c cc axes trong figure
  • linewidth quy nh dy ca khung vin ny
  • facecolor quy nh mu nn ca figure

Tip: Gi tr mc nh ca chng nh sau: edgecolor='w', linewidth=0, facecolor='w'. V th, nu ta ch thay i mu edgecolor th vn cha thy khung vin ny, m ta cn phi tng gi tr linewidth ln dpi phn gii ca hnh (dots per inch). Gi tr mc nh l 100. dpi cng cao th cht lng nh s cng cao

Lưu figure¶

lu mt figure ta dng phng thc savefig( ) trong lp Figure:

In [8]:
fig.savefig("Hello.png")

Ta c mt file nh Hello.png:

Chng ta c th ty chn ch nh DPI v cc nh dng u ra khc nhau (PNG, JPG, EPS, SVG, PGF and PDF):

In [9]:
fig.savefig("Hello2.png", dpi = 640)

Mt s lu khi s dng.

Gi s ta v hnh sau y trn mt figure c nn mu xm nh sau:

In [10]:
# Khi to hai mng ngu nhin X v Y
n = 100
X = np.random.rand(n)
Y = np.random.rand(n)

# Din tch s tng dn theo trc Y
area = 100 * Y**2 * np.pi

# Mu sc s thay i theo trc X
colors = X

# Khi to mt figure trng c nn xm
fig = plt.figure(facecolor='#00000050', dpi = 640)

# Gi phng thc gca() (get curent axes) ca fig
# Sau  v ln axes nhn c
fig.gca().scatter(X, Y, s=area, c=colors, cmap=plt.cm.jet, edgecolor='k')
# fig.show()
Out[10]:
<matplotlib.collections.PathCollection at 0x1bc41630fa0>

Phng thc gca() dng gi n axes ang trng thi active trong figure. Nu figure cha c axes no th gca() s to ra mt axes mi, tng ng vi add_subplot(111)

By gi th lu figure trn bng lnh fig.savefig('random points.png'). Ta s thu c PNG sau:

In [11]:
fig.savefig('random points.png', dpi = 360)

Nn xm ca figure b bin thnh mu trng. Nguyn nhn l method savefig() cng c tham s facecolor (mc nh mu trng) v tham s ny over-ride ( ln) facecolor ca figure.

lu c figure ng nh ta nhn thy trn ca s figure ta phi ly facecolor ca figure bng phng thc get_facecolor(), tng t nh sau:

In [12]:
fig.savefig('random points.png', facecolor=fig.get_facecolor(), dpi = 360)

Tng t, cc tham s edgecolor, dpi cng phi c khai bo trong lnh savefig gi ng nguyn trng ca figure.

In [13]:
fig.savefig('random points.png', 
            facecolor=fig.get_facecolor(), 
            edgecolor=fig.get_edgecolor(),
            dpi = fig.get_dpi())

Note: Sau khi show hnh ln, nu ta zoom hnh, co dn ca s, di chuyn hnh v (bng cng c move), th nhng tc ng ny cng trc tip lm thay i figure (tc l ta thy figure th no th sau khi savefig ta cng s c nh th ). Do , nu bn c rt nhiu figure, cn chnh cc figure ny cho thng nht, ta khng nn cn chnh bng tay. M phi cn chnh thng qua cc tham s khi khi to v khi lu figure.

Xóa nội dung một figure¶

Xa ni dung ca mt figure tc l xa i cc axes v hnh v gn lin vi cc axes . Vic ny l cn thit trong mt s trng hp, thay v phi khi to ra figure mi v ln.

C 3 cch xa ni dung ca mt figure. Gi s ta cn xa ni dung ca fig:

  • fig.clf()
  • clear()
  • plt.clf()

Cch th nht v th hai l hon ton ging nhau, v thc cht phng thc clear() s gi n clf(). Cch th 3 ch c tc dng khi fig ang active

Một số ý quan trọng trong bài:¶

  • Figure l i tng ca python. V mt trc quan th mt figure l mt ca s cha cc hnh v,
  • Figure c mt hoc nhiu axes ni thc s cc hnh v c gn ln
  • ly danh sch cc axes ca figure, ta gi phng thc get_axes() t i tng figure
  • Khi lu hnh v bng phng thc savefig, phi ch vic over-ride cc thuc tnh ca *figure
  • Figure cho php xa cc axes thuc v n bng phng thc clear()
